# 🧮 Calculator Program in C

## 📌 Project Overview
This project is a simple Calculator Program developed in the C programming language as part of the **CodeAlpha C Programming Internship – Task 1**. It performs basic arithmetic operations using the **switch-case** statement.

## 🎯 Objective
To build a menu-driven calculator that performs basic mathematical operations:
- Addition
- Subtraction
- Multiplication
- Division

## ✨ Features
- User-friendly menu
- Uses `switch-case` for operation selection
- Supports four basic arithmetic operations
- Handles invalid menu choices
- Simple and easy-to-understand code

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- C Programming
- GCC Compiler / Turbo C / Code::Blocks / VS Code

